## FAQs

**Is a redesign the answer to my Google ranking drop?**
Probably not on its own. Algorithm penalties are usually content quality, E-E-A-T, or backlink issues. Run an [algorithm update recovery audit](/services/google-algorithm-update-recovery/) before paying for a redesign.

**Can you fix a Wix or Squarespace site without rebuilding?**
Limited. UX and content fixes, yes. Core Web Vitals and schema, partially. Full SEO retrofit usually requires moving off Wix.

**How long does a UX fix sprint take?**
Two to three weeks from kickoff to launch.

**Do I need new content for a UX rebuild?**
Often no — the existing copy can be tightened in place. The single biggest lever is usually structure, not new words.

